appropriate. <br>
<br>
- Salvage values based on the value of the object has been set on <br>
existing quest armor and weapons. <br>
<br>
- The Cloak of Night can now take emblems. <br>
<br>
- The Emerald-beaded strand now has the correct icon. <br>
<br>
CRAFTING SYSTEM NOTES <br>
<br>
