even chance that any crafted item will have a quality of 94-99 percent, with <br>
a very small chance of 100 percent. <br>
<br>
- When you go up in level in a crafting skill, the print line will now tell you <br>
what your new level is. <br>
<br>
- Added in the ability for armorcrafters and tailors to make the &quot;level 6&quot; <br>
